    "translation":{"eng":"The lotus feet of the venerable Vaiṣṇavas are the greatest treasure in the world. O brother, please listen with rapt attention. Śrī Kṛṣṇa never forsakes one who, having taken shelter of the Vaiṣṇavas, lovingly worships Him. All others perish without purpose."}},{
