    "translation":{"eng":"There is nothing more powerful than water that has washed the lotus feet of a Vaiṣṇava, to give the strength to attain prema-bhakti. There is no greater ornament than the dust of the lotus feet of a Vaiṣṇava to serve as the ornament for one’s head."}},{
