    "translation":{"eng":"The purifying qualities of water from holy places are written in the Purāṇas, but all this cheats one of [the wealth of] bhakti. Actually, the water from holy places is not as purifying as water that has washed the feet of Vaiṣṇavas, by which one’s desires are fulfilled."}},{
